          "contents": "# TODO - Add a parameter to the function\ndef new_follower_alert():\n  # Prints a welcome message to a follower\n\n  # TODO - Update the print statement to use the parameter\n  print(\"Welcome, streamer123!\")\n\n# TODO - Call the function with a name\nnew_follower_alert()\n",
